introduction: Conor McCullagh from "Face Off" is one of the contestants on the Syfy reality special effects make-up artist competition series. Conor ("Face Off") is from Mississauga, Ontario, Canada. He is 40 years old.Conor McCullagh has worked on special effects and/or make-up for The CW's "The Vampire Diaries" as well as movies such as "Big Mommas: Like Father, Like Son," "The Killing Jar," "Stan Helsing," "A Dirty Shame," "Jackass: The Movie," "Shallow Hal," "Osmosis Jones," "Say It Isn't So," "Scary Movie 2" and "Freddy Got Fingered."
